    // Aries - 6 inclusive and concrete variations
    "prediction100.aries.var0": "Over the next 100 days, your energy and courage will be your allies. At work, you may be called to initiate something new, like proposing an original idea or leading a small project, which will stimulate your sense of action. In love, if you are single, an outing or hobby could help you meet someone who shares your enthusiasm, perhaps the start of a romance. If you are in a relationship, enjoying a small adventure together, a getaway, a class, or a shared activity will strengthen your bond. In daily life, remember to balance effort with rest to avoid burnout.",
    "prediction100.aries.var1": "These weeks will be an excellent time to set personal goals. At work, you might surprise yourself by progressing faster than expected on tasks you thought would be long or tedious, giving you a real sense of accomplishment. In love, if you are single, even without an immediate encounter, getting to know yourself better will provide valuable clarity for the future; if you are in a relationship, sharing your future plans (vacations, personal goals) will bring you closer and spark meaningful conversations. Regarding health, make sure to get good sleep on days when you feel tired.",
    "prediction100.aries.var2": "The coming months invite you to balance your life rhythm. At work, you may face unexpected events that test your adaptability, such as handling a sudden problem or helping a colleague last minute, but your responsiveness and boldness will help you bounce back. In love, if you are single, this may be a more introspective period: enjoy the freedom to be yourself and learn from each interaction; if you are in a relationship, a cozy moment at home, like cooking together or planning an outing, will strengthen your connection. In daily life, finding moments of calm, even brief ones, will do you a lot of good.",
    "prediction100.aries.var3": "During these 100 days, you may experience bursts of energy followed by periods of fatigue. At work, this could mean intense activity spurts followed by days when you need to slow down: learning to listen to your body and take strategic breaks will help you stay effective. In love, if you are single, someone you already know may suddenly seem more interesting, a subtle but meaningful connection; if you are in a relationship, spontaneous moments of tenderness (a surprise message, a shared smile) will bring warmth and joy to your daily life. Personally, remember to stay hydrated and take deep breaths when stress rises.",
    "prediction100.aries.var4": "These weeks may encourage you to experiment and learn. At work, a new skill or method could capture your attention and give you renewed momentum; developing your knowledge or testing a different tool will stimulate you. In love, if you are single, an unexpected encounter in a group or social activity could bring a delightful surprise. If you are in a relationship, achieving a small goal together (completing a shared project, planning a long-awaited outing) will strengthen your bond. In social life, light-hearted moments with friends will help you relax and keep your joy alive.",
    "prediction100.aries.var5": "The next 100 days invite you to channel your energy into concrete actions. At work, you may find that breaking your tasks into small steps makes you calmer and more efficient. In love, if you are single, learning to enjoy simple moments with someone (a walk, coffee, shared laughter) will be very rewarding; if you are in a relationship, an end-of-day ritual or a shared hobby will help you create beautiful memories. In daily life, thinking about balancing leisure and responsibilities will help you maintain motivation.",
    // Taurus - 6 inclusive and concrete variations
    "prediction100.taurus.var0": "The next 100 days will be marked by stability and small pleasant surprises. At work, you may be asked to finalize an important project, collaborate with a new team, or organize a key meeting. In love, if you are single, an unexpected encounter could brighten your day, possibly the start of an unexpected relationship; if you are in a relationship, taking time to plan shared activities or discuss future projects will strengthen your bond. In friendship, someone close may need your support or share a special moment with you. Personally, find moments to relax and enjoy simple pleasures.",
    "prediction100.taurus.var1": "This period invites patience and reflection. At work, you may need to manage multiple responsibilities at once, such as handling unexpected requests or helping a colleague solve a problem. In love, if you are single, a closer connection with someone in your circle is possible—a person you never thought might interest you, but with whom a real connection could emerge. If you are in a relationship, discussions about daily organization or sharing responsibilities will strengthen your bond. In friendship, you may be asked for advice or to support a loved one in an important decision. Personally, take time for yourself to recenter and enjoy your hobbies.",
