    // Pisces - 6 inclusive and concrete variations
    "prediction100.pisces.var0": "The next 100 days could be a journey of delicate emotions and inner discoveries. At work, you may be inspired by a creative idea or a new way to approach a project that excites you, even if some days demand more focus. In love, if you are single, a connection could grow from an existing friendship or during an artistic or spiritual activity; if you are in a relationship, shared moments like talking about dreams or watching favorite movies together will strengthen your bond. In daily life, take breaks to recharge, like a peaceful walk or a moment of meditation.",
    "prediction100.pisces.var1": "During these weeks, intuition and sensitivity will be your allies. At work, you may be called to listen and understand colleagues or help resolve a misunderstanding, which will strengthen others’ trust in your approach. In love, if you are single, you might enjoy inner peace and self-knowledge more than seeking a romantic encounter right away; if you are in a relationship, simple shared moments, like cooking together or discussing deep feelings, will bring you closer. For health, balance your emotional energy by getting enough rest.",
    "prediction100.pisces.var2": "These 100 days will be an opportunity to explore creativity and spirituality. At work, you may find pleasure in tasks that allow you to express imagination or attention to detail, like a presentation, creation, or new format. In love, if you are single, a light yet meaningful connection could emerge during a workshop, class, or artistic activity; if you are in a relationship, planning a cultural outing or a joint artistic activity will revitalize your bond. Socially, a friend may invite you to an experience that broadens your perspectives.",
    "prediction100.pisces.var3": "During this period, you may feel alternating intense emotional energy and need for calm. At work, some weeks may feel busy or rich in exchanges, while others call for slowing down and stepping back. In love, if you are single, you may feel drawn to someone you already know, but the true richness lies in emotional connection rather than speed; if you are in a relationship, sharing a quiet moment together, like a walk or stress-free dinner, will strengthen mutual trust. Personally, listen to your body: if fatigue shows, don’t hesitate to slow down and rest.",
    "prediction100.pisces.var4": "These 100 days invite you to turn sensitivity into strength. At work, you may be called to support someone going through a tough time or clarify a delicate situation, highlighting your compassion and calmness. In love, if you are single, you may grow closer to someone through a shared interest or a sincere moment together; if you are in a relationship, a gentle activity like a creative moment or deep discussion will strengthen your bond. For well-being, find moments of silence, music, or relaxation to maintain emotional balance.",
    "prediction100.pisces.var5": "The coming months will be an opportunity to show insight and empathy. At work, a situation that seemed confusing may become clear thanks to your intuition and ability to see what others miss. In love, if you are single, a beautiful friendship may evolve into something deeper, without rush—the emotional connection is what truly matters; if you are in a relationship, a shared project, like organizing a weekend or planning a hobby together, will strengthen your bond. For health, include a gentle routine (yoga, stretches, walks) to maintain your energy.",

